## API sketch

```ts
export interface RenderOptions {
  strict?: boolean;
  theme?: "default" | "dark";
}
```

::callout{tone="warning"}
Document any unsafe escape hatches and make strict rendering the default in CI.
::

::decision{id="spec-decision" status="proposed" owner="engineering"}
Use the smallest public API that supports the first production workflow.
::

